quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  2,6,"Ndithudi iwo amene sakhulupilira ndi chimodzimodzi kwa iwo kaya iwe uwachenjeza kapena osawachenjeza, ndipo iwo sadzakhulupilira"
  2,7,"Mulungu waika chophimba m’mitima mwawo ndi m’makutu mwawo, ndi m’maso mwawo muli chovindikira. Ndipo chawo chidzakhala chilango chachikulu"
  2,8,"Pakati pa anthu alipo amene amanena kuti: “Ife tikhulupirira mwa Mulungu ndi tsiku la chiweruzo” pamene iwo sali anthu okhulupirira ngakhale pang’ono"
  2,9,Iwo amangofuna kunamiza Mulungu ndi iwo amene amakhulupirira mwa Iye. Koma iwo sanamiza wina aliyense kupatula kudzinamiza okha ngakhale kuti iwo sazindikira
  2,10,M’mitima mwawo muli matenda ndipo Mulungu wawonjezera. Iwo adzalangidwa kwambiri chifukwa cha chinyengo chawo
  2,11,"Ndipo zikanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Musachite zoipa m’dziko,” iwo amayankha kuti: “Ndithudi ife ndi ochita zabwino.”"
  2,12,Ndithudi! Iwo ndiwo amene amachita zoipa koma kuti iwo sazindikira
  2,13,"Ndipo zikanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Khulupirirani monga momwe anthu akhulupirira.” Iwo amayankha kuti: “Kodi ife tikhulupirire monga momwe zitsiru zikhulupirira?” Ndithudi iwo ndiwo zitsiru koma iwo sazindikira"
  2,14,"Ndipo iwo akakumana ndi anthu okhulupirira, amanena kuti: “Ife timakhulupilira!” Koma akakhala okha pakati pa a Satana awo amati: “Ndithudi ife tili ndi inu. Ndithudi ife timangowasyasyalika chabe.”"
  2,15,Mulungu amawasyasyalika iwo ndipo amawasiya nthawi yaitali mu uchimo ndi kumapitirirabe kuchimwa mwaumbuli
  2,16,Amenewa ndiwo amene agula chisokonekero m’malo mwa njira yoyenera. Iwo sanapindule pa malonda awo. Ndipo sanali wotsogozedwa